title: BREAKING: DPNM Chairwoman on Secretary of State Duran’s Resignation (Democratic Party of New Mexico)
text: ( Source : Democratic Party of New Mexico ) The Secretary of State 's office released a statement late Thursday night announcing the resignation of Secretary Duran , as well as the cancellation of the rulemaking hearings scheduled for Friday,
